        \u003Ccountry>Italy\u003C/country>\n                        \u003Cregion>Sicily\u003C/region>\n                        \u003Csettlement>Lipari\u003C/settlement>\n                        \u003Crepository>Castello\u003C/repository>\n                        \u003C!--Adding location for old id numbers if available-->\n                        \u003CaltIdentifier>\n                            \u003Csettlement/>\n                            \u003Crepository/>\n                            \u003Cidno type=\"old\"/>\n                        \u003C/altIdentifier>\n                    \u003C/msIdentifier>\n                    \u003CmsContents>\n                        \u003CtextLang mainLang=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/textLang>\n                    \u003C/msContents>\n                    \u003CphysDesc>\n                        \u003CobjectDesc>\n                            \u003CsupportDesc>\n                                \u003Csupport>\n                                    \u003Cp>The cippus is carefully squared and with well-polished surfaces. Chipped at the left corner of the front face, at the upper corners and along the lower edge of the back face. The right side face has an irregular surface (intentionally chipped?) with remains of mortar\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cmaterial ana=\"#material.stone.volcanic\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/28.html\">volcanic (probably coming from colata di Fuardo)\u003C/material>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.stele\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/250\">stele\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\u003C!--ILipara-->\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\">30\u003C/height>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\">43\u003C/width>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\">31\u003C/depth>\n                                    \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003C/support>\n                                \u003Ccondition/>\n                            \u003C/supportDesc>\n                            \u003ClayoutDesc>\n                                \u003Clayout>\n                                    \u003Crs ana=\"#execution.chiselled\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1\">chiselled\u003C/rs>\n                                    \u003Cdamage/>\n                                \u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\u003C!--ILipara-->\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line1\">Line 1\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"35\" atMost=\"37\">35-37\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\u003Cregion>Sicilia\u003C/region>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462283\">Lipara\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/2524378\">Lipari\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003Cgeo>38.48333, 14.93333\u003C/geo>\n                            \u003C/origPlace>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\" subtype=\"discovered\">The stone comes from the Castello, but the exact place, date and circumstances of discovery are not known. Kept inside the bell tower of the Cathedral, currently located in the cloister\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\">None\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition/>\n                    \u003C/history>\n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n            \u003Cp>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines\u003C/p>\n            \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                    \u003Cp>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/xi:fallback>\n            \u003C/xi:include>\n            \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n                \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                    \u003Cp>ISicily glyphs authority list\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/xi:fallback>\n            \u003C/xi:include>\n        \u003C/encodingDesc>\n        \u003CprofileDesc>\n            \u003CcalendarDesc>\n                \u003Ccalendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    \u003Cp>Julian Calendar\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/calendar>\n            \u003C/calendarDesc>\n            \u003ClangUsage>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"en\">English\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"it\">Italian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"la\">Latin\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"he\">Hebrew\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"phn\">Phoenician\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xpu\">Punic\u003C/language>\n               